UID:8Ax8XR7ANzQAQZ9vB_kto
SUMMARY:Keep Bellevue Beautiful - Newport
DTSTAMP:20260404T043957Z
DTSTART:20260404T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Keep Bellevue Beautiful - Newport\n\nEReed\n\nTue\, 03/10/2026 
	- 15:45\n\nApril 4 2026\n\n9:00 AM - 11:00 AM\n\nAll Day Event\n\nOff\n\nE
	vent Registration\n\nFree\n\nContact\n\nEvan Reed\n\nEmail\n\nereed@bellev
	uewa.gov\n\nTelephone\n\n425-452-5372\n\nLocation\n\nNewport Hills Park\, 
	6029 120th Ave SE\n\nDescription\n\nThe City of Bellevue's Keep Bellevue B
	eautiful program is launching\n\n26 in '26\,\n\nan effort aimed at complet
	ing\n\n26 Signature Street cleanups\n\nin 2026. The goal is simple: show u
