BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:PSY9NvdZ3oUdOKMq3v5eW
SUMMARY:TOKI - The Japanese ELVIS
DTSTAMP:20260404T043959Z
DTSTART:20260418T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:You know him! You love him! Returning for his 3rd straight year
	 to Georgetown\, Seattle... Performing at the historic Jules Maes Saloon..
	. Co-Sponored by Jellyfish Brewing & Sound Goods Canned Wine... It's.... T
	OKI\, the Japanese ELVIS!!!\n\nRecently crowned Top 5 in the World Elvis U
	ltimate Tribute Artist at the House of the King \\(Graceland\\)\, makes hi
	s 2026 return! This is 21\\+show on Friday\, April 17th at 6PM \\(Doors at
	 5PM\\) at Jules Maes Saloon in Georgetown. $15 ADV / $20 DAY OF: https://
	tickets.venuepilot.com/.../toki-the-japanese...\n\nHailing from the Land o
	f the Rising Sun\, Toki discovered his love for performing at the age of 1
	4. A lunch break while working construction jobs at the age of 21 proved p
	ivotal to his career as it was then that he fell in love with the King of 
	Rock & Roll. Toki often spent his breaks at Tower Records and one day\, El
	vis ’56 ruled the store’s TVs. So mesmerized was Toki\, that he only retur
	ned to his job when the foreman bought him the VHS tape so he would leave 
	the store. The rest was history!\n\nToki made his inaugural international 
	performance back in 2007 at The Cavern Bar in Dallas\, TX to a packed hous
	e\, and found his calling. He has returned almost every year to perform in
	 numerous cities across the US and all over the world!\n\nOn top of his Gr
	aceland achievement\, Toki has won many global competitions\, including as
	 the first foreigner to win the famed Branson contest in 2023 and a previo
	us victory in Parkes\, Australia. He has been featured in the New York Tim
	es\, Reuters\, and many more world-wide publications.\n\nNow focused on ke
	eping Elvis’ memory alive across the globe\, Toki may not speak English\, 
	but he can sing the hell out of some Elvis!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.co
	m/events/#/details/toki-the-japanese-elvis/18478909/2026-04-17T00\n\nFrom 
	SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/toki-the-japanese-elvis/1
	8478909/2026-04-17T00
LOCATION:Jules Maes Saloon\, 5919 Airport Wy S\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT4H
END:VEVENT
